# Modification Log - Database Migration + DeepSeek V4 Pro + pgvector RAG

## Overview
This document tracks all changes made to transform the project from a document-based system to a product-centric system with vector search capabilities using DeepSeek V4 Pro.

**Date**: 2026-05-08
**Project**: Gomedia IA Specifications
**Goal**: Migrate to product-based schema with RAG capabilities

